00915         enum E {
00916                 LeftDown = 0x1,
00917                 LeftHeld = 0x2,
00918                 LeftUp = 0x4,
00919                 Move = 0x8,
00920                 RightDown = 0x10,
00921                 RightHeld = 0x20,
00922                 RightUp = 0x40
00923         } _;
00924 
00925         public:
00926                 MouseEvent(unsigned char val) { this->_ = static_cast<E>(val); };
